$$ param file: savile-row/test-instances/test_comprehension_functions.eprime.param

language ESSENCE' 1.0

letting n_nurses be 6
letting Demand be  [[1,0,1,0],
                [0,0,1,0],
		[1,2,0,0],
		[1,0,0,0],
		[1,0,1,0],
		[1,0,1,0],
